Description: LOC (Linked Open Commerce) is a collaboration of OpenLink Software- Hepp Research GmbH and Linktegration that delivers a structured Linked Data space on the Web for finding products and services related offers- with precision.This project seeks to provide a Linked Data substrate that delivers a foundation for new kinds of e-commerce applications and services.### IssuesThe SPARQL endpoint also contains other- not e-Commerce related- RDF data collected from the Web.
